Package com.amplifyframework.core.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Model
    All models should conform to the Model interface.
    ModelProvider
    Defines the contract for retrieving information about the models generated for DataStoreCategoryBehavior.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthRule
    AuthRule is used define an authorization rule for who can access and operate against a Model or a ModelField.
    AuthRule.Builder
    Builder class for AuthRule.
    ModelAssociation
    Represents an association of the Model class.
    ModelAssociation.Builder
    Builder class for ModelAssociation.
    ModelField
    Represents a field of the Model class.
    ModelField.ModelFieldBuilder
    Builder class for ModelField.
    ModelIndex
    Attributes of a Model.
    ModelIndex.Builder
    The builder class for ModelIndex.Builder.
    ModelSchema
    Schema of a Model that implements the Model interface.
    ModelSchema.Builder
    The Builder to build the ModelSchema object.
    ModelSchemaRegistry
    A utility that creates ModelSchema from Model classes.
    PrimaryKey
    The PrimaryKey of a data model is the field with the name "id".
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AuthStrategy
    The type of strategy for an @auth directive rule.
    ModelOperation
    Used as a property of AuthRule to specify which operations the rule applies to.
